Title: 011: Learning Resources, Thinking Like a Data Scientist and Data Exploration with Garth Zoller
Description:
In this session of the Super Data Science Podcast, I chat with Aspiring Data Scientist Garth Zoller. You will know how a creative person ends up in data science, discover how organisations build a culture of data science and be able to walk through an interesting case study on how Garth deals with vague business problems.


If you enjoyed this episode, check out show notes, resources, and more at www.superdatascience.com/11
